5C%22%5C%22%3Eprofit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I'm%20betting%20between%20%2450%20and%20%24100%20to%20win%20%243%20to%20%244%2C%20but%20it%20all%20adds%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20returns%20I'm%20getting%2C%20I%20needed%20initial%20capital%20of%20about%20%2420%2C000%20and%20maybe%20one%20to%20two%20hours%20per%20day.%20But%20anyone%20can%20really%20be%20profitable%20with%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20game%20is%20maximizing%20your%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20so%20the%20more%20that%20you%20put%20in%2C%20the%20more%20profitable%20you%20will%20be.%20Each%20one%20of%20the%20bets%20you're%20making%20is%20going%20to%20have%20a%20profit%20margin%20between%203%25%20and%204%25%20%E2%80%94%20so%20if%20you%20have%20%241%2C000%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20make%20%2430%20or%20%2440%20bucks.%20If%20you%20only%20have%20%24100%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20make%20%243%20or%20%244.%20Even%20paying%20for%20the%20subscription%20to%20OddsJam%2C%20it%20really%20does%20pay%20for%20itself%20very%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273415262-d684-45d4-98e8-fe9f29e0e77c%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20catch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%20arbitrage%20betting%20is%20legal%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20state%20you're%20in%2C%20but%20of%20course%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-gambling-weird-quirks-bets-nfl-nba-draftkings-fanduel-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esportsbook%20sites%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20really%20like%20it%20because%20they're%20losing%20money.%20Each%20platform%20has%20different%20terms%20of%20service%2C%20but%20when%20they%20catch%20you%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20they%20will%20because%20they%20have%20algorithms%20dedicated%20to%20detecting%20these%20kinds%20of%20bets%20%E2%80%94%20your%20account%20will%20probably%20get%20restricted%20so%20you%20can't%20bet%20as%20much%20money.%20That%20means%20you'll%20have%20to%20play%20more%20often%20or%20bet%20on%20more%20games%20to%20see%20the%20same%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20betting%20on%20very%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funusual-sports-around-the-world-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eobscure%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20aren't%20usually%20bet%20on%20%E2%80%94%20like%20you're%20betting%20%242%2C000%20that%20some%20cricket%20game%20in%20India%20is%20going%20to%20go%20a%20certain%20way%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they're%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20you're%20probably%20arbitraging.%20So%20you%20can%20kind%20of%20mitigate%20the%20risk%20by%20not%20taking%20bets%20that%20are%20super%20obscure%20and%20just%20doing%20more%20main%20lines%20that%20are%20very%2C%20very%20common%2C%20which%20will%20help%20you%20remain%20undetected%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20you%20could%20probably%20last%20a%20week%20or%20two%20on%20average%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-odds-gambling-lines-memecoins-prediction-markets-polymarket-stocks-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecasinos%3C%2Fa%3E%20catch%20on.%20I%20lasted%20around%20two%20weeks%20on%20most%20of%20my%20sports%20books%2C%20but%20there%20were%20a%20couple%20that%20got%20me%20within%20three%20or%20four%20days%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20be%20super%20profitable%20on%20them%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20fun%20in%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20days%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20bigger%20bets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'd%20think%20it%20would%20probably%20be%20in%20the%20site's%20best%20interest%20to%20disband%20your%20account%20if%20you%20were%20just%20exploiting%20them%20and%20taking%20money%20from%20them.%20But%2C%20as%20arbitrage%20betters%2C%20we%20actually%20do%20provide%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20value%20to%20the%20sportsbook%20sites%2C%20because%20they%20can%20study%20an%20arbitrage%20player's%20activity%20for%20signals%20on%20where%20they%20can%20tighten%20up%20their