complicated%2C%20so%20my%20roommate%20and%20I%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesharpreview.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20social%20media%20channels%20to%20teach%20other%20people%20our%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20is%20taxes.%20Every%20state%20and%20player%20is%20different%2C%20but%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20know%20that%20I'll%20have%20to%20pay%20taxes%20of%20around%2020%25%20of%20my%20earnings.%20So%20I've%20accounted%20for%20that%2C%20and%20I%20put%20that%20portion%20in%20a%20fund%20that's%20allocated%20to%20low-risk%20stocks%2C%20so%20hopefully%20I%20don't%20lose%20any%20of%20that%20money.%20But%20even%20taking%20that%20money%20into%20account%2C%20it%20feels%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20assuming%20I'll%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20this%20going%20because%20my%20roommate's%20been%20doing%20it%20for%20years%2C%20and%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20remain%20profitable.%20So%20there's%20no%20end%20in%20sight%2C%20hopefully.%20I'm%20hoping%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frising-stars-sports-betting-and-gaming-at-draftkings-fanduel-more-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewinnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20a%20house%2C%20a%20wedding%20ring%20for%20my%20girlfriend%2C%20a%20new%20car%2C%20or%20just%2C%20you%20know%2C%20a%20fallback%20fund%20if%20things%20go%20really%20south%20and%20I%20lose%20my%20job%20or%20something%20like%20that%20especially%20with%20the%20economy%20the%20way%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20no%20idea%20exactly%20where%20I'll%20spend%20the%20money%2C%20but%20my%20plan%20is%20to%20save%20it%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgambling-young-men-sports-betting-crypto-meme-stock-market-addiction-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvest%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20wisely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%2