emergency%20tracheotomy%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20true%20%26quot%3BMission%3A%20Impossible%26quot%3B%20style%2C%20Ethan%20retrieves%20the%20Poison%20Pill%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20as%20Gabriel%20falls%20out%20of%20the%20plane%20and%20dies.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20the%20plane%20catches%20fire%2C%20and%20Ethan%20has%20to%20leap%20out%20of%20the%20vehicle%20and%20put%20the%20source%20code%20into%20the%20Poison%20Pill%20while%20falling%20through%20the%20air%2C%20because%20nothing%20is%20ever%20easy%20in%20this%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20he%20manages%20to%20pull%20it%20off%2C%20and%20Grace%20uses%20her%20quick%20reflexes%20to%20yank%20a%20glorified%20USB%20stick%20out%20of%20the%20console%20in%20the%20bunker%20to%20permanently%20trap%20the%20Entity.%20In%20the%20film's%20final%20moments%2C%20the%20IMF%20team%20meets%20up%20again%20in%20London%20as%20Grace%20gives%20Ethan%20the%20stick%20containing%20the%20Entity%20for%20safekeeping.%20They%20all%20share%20an%20emotional%20look%20at%20one%20another%20before%20going%20their%20separate%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20shot%20doesn't%20definitively%20end%20the%20franchise%2C%20and%20leaves%20the%20door%20open%20for%20the%20cast%20to%20return%20(should%20they%20choose%20to%20accept)%20for%20another%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20a%20little%20weird%2C%20since%20the%20film%20was%20billed%20to%20be%20an%20ending%20to%20the%20franchise.%20Here%20are%20the%20lingering%20questions%20we%20have%20about%20%26quot%3BThe%20Final%20Reckoning%26quot%3B%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229244b28c-8d7e-41bd-8899-96ee0ff41fd0%5C%22%3EWas%20Ethan%20Hunt%20supposed%20to%20die%20at%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BMission%3A%20Impossible%20-%20The%20Final%20Reckoning%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20a%20brown%20leather%20jacket%2C%20white%20t-shirt%2C%20brown%20pants%2C%20and%20boots%20dangling%20from%20a%20yellow%20bipla