US%20bond%20yields%20is%20overblown%2C%20said%20a%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20referring%20to%20yields%20on%2010-%20and%2030-year%20US%20Treasurys%2C%20which%20rose%20as%20high%20as%204.6%25%20and%205.2%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20this%20past%20week.%20The%20increases%20came%20after%20the%20decision%20by%20Moody's%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreasury-yields-moodys-rating-downgrade-us-economy-trump-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edowngrade%20its%20rating%20on%20US%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20May%2016%2C%20and%20accelerated%20in%20the%20following%20week%20on%20concerns%20over%20the%20sweeping%20budget%20bill%20advancing%20through%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20commentators%20have%20said%20fears%20about%20the%20swelling%20budget%20deficit%20are%20behind%20the%20week's%20bond-market%20jitters%2C%20Jim%20Caron%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20the%20portfolio%20solutions%20group%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsell-america-stock-bond-market-annual-forward-outlook-morgan-stanley-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fa%3E%20Investment%20Management%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20thinks%20the%20issue%20is%20being%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20markets%20were%20already%20aware%20that%20the%20national%20deficit%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20so%20Trump's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-beautiful-bill-medicaid-taxes-maga-accounts-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebig%20beautiful%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20passed%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20on%20Thursday%20isn't%20really%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaron%20said%20he%20refers%20to%20those%20who%20believe%20Treasurys%20could%20lose%20their%20safe-haven%20status%20as%20%26quot%3Btourists%20in%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5