%2C%26quot%3B%20Caron%20said%20of%20the%20deficit%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Morgan%20Stanley%20strategist%20argued%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-yields-rising-japan-us-deficit-spending-debt-carry-trade-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erising%20bond%20yields%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20global%20issue%2C%20and%20not%20just%20a%20US%20problem.%20Long-dated%20bonds%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20Japan%20have%20soared%20this%20year%20on%20fears%20over%20those%20countries'%20fiscal%20outlooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20find%20it%20to%20be%20a%20very%20novice%20explanation%20when%20people%20say%2C%20'oh%2C%20I%20think%20the%20US%20is%20losing%20its%20status%20and%20the%20dollar%20is%20going%20to%20lose%20its%20reserve%20status%2C'%26quot%3B%20Caron%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20that%20were%20actually%20even%201%25%20true%2C%20the%20markets%20would%20be%20selling%20off%20in%20a%20massive%2C%20massive%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbond-market-treasurys-panic-overhyped-morgan-stanley-jim-caron-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748083113000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830c302c6ad288d1481d135%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbond-market-treasurys-panic-overhyped-morgan-stanley-jim-caron-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jim%20Caron%20of%20Morgan%20Stanley%20rejected%20fears%20that%20Treasurys%20were%20no%20longer%20safe%20havens%20and%20said%20rising%20bond%20yields%20were%20a%20global%20issue%2C%20not%20just%20a%20US%20problem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nredmond%40insider.com%20(Nora%20Redmond)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbond-market-treasurys-panic-overhyped-morgan-stanley-jim-caron-2025-5%22%2C%22c