sons%20widely.%20He%20wants%20to%20write%20a%20book%20with%2010%20principles%20for%20combating%20%26quot%3Binflammaging%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20inflammatory%20processes%20that%20can%20creep%20up%20on%20us%20as%20we%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20trying%20to%20develop%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buckinstitute.org%2Fblog%2Fa-healthy-selfie-may-be-in-your-future%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etool%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20anyone%20can%20use%20to%20help%20assess%20how%20well%20their%20body%20is%20aging%2C%20for%20free.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20tests%20out%20there%20promising%20to%20help%20you%20calculate%20your%20biological%20age%2C%20and%20many%20different%20ways%20to%20measure%20it%20(some%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-36-ai-test-novos-said-face-age-is-39-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edubious%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20others).%20Furman%20is%20interested%20in%20using%20photos%20of%20a%20person's%20face%20as%20an%20accessible%20way%20to%20gauge%20their%20rate%20of%20aging%2C%20a%20technique%20that%20medical%20researchers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flandig%2Farticle%2FPIIS2589-7500(25)00042-1%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMass%20General%20Brigham%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20trying%20out%20for%20informing%20cancer%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fish%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679bf0227bb3f854015b4181%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEating%20fatty%20fish%20can%20help%20reduce%20inflammation%20and%20improve%20brain%20health.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Furman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2265af9e65-1d66-4bd5-97ee-07c9702fe6f0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlending%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20city%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFurman%20doesn't%20suggest%20that%20he's%20cracked%20the%2