ention%20and%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20garage%20to%20Amazon%3A%20The%20brand%E2%80%99s%20expansion%20over%20the%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20garage%20start-up%20to%20a%20nationally%20recognised%20sustainability%20brand%2C%20Bare%20Necessities%20is%20growing%20steadily.%20They%20now%20serve%20customers%20both%20directly%20(D2C)%20via%20their%20website%20and%20platforms%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Flipkart%2C%20and%20businesses%20(B2B)%20through%20corporate%20gifting%20and%20bulk%20orders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-19_11zon-1747976118.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entire%20team%20at%20Bare%20Necessities%20supports%20each%20other%20and%20is%20dedicated%20to%20manufacturing%20eco-friendly%20products%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-19_11zon-1747976118.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-19_11zon-1747976118-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-19_11zon-1747976118-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-19_11zon-1747976118-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-19_11zon-1747976118-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-437264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20entire%20team%20at%20Bare%20Necessities%20supports%20each%20other%20and%20is%20dedicated%20to%20manufacturing%20eco-friendly%20products%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E